<b>2.</b> Population  in  <b>Metropolitan Areas</b>, 1970-1990
<p><center>
<table border>
<tr>
<th></th><td>1970</td><td>1980</td><td>1990</td>
</tr>
<tr><td>Population (millions)</td><td>159.6</td><td>176.9</td><td>197.7</td>
</tr></table></center>
<p>



