<DOCHDR>
http://www.lead-inst.org:80/townhall/FRC/fampol/fp95ied.html 204.71.237.80 19970210142924 text/html 42146
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Monday, 10-Feb-97 14:30:09 GMT
Last-modified: Sunday, 31-Mar-96 23:46:23 GMT
