<p>

<li>Charles Murray, &quot;The Coming White Underclass,&quot;
<I>The Wall Street Journal</I>, October 29, 1993.

<p>

<li>Research by Irwin Garfinkel and Sara S. McLanahan at the
University of Wisconsin, cited in Matthew Robinson, &quot;Can
