thereof . . .&quot;
<p>
<li><i>Religion in the Public Schools:  A Joint Statement of Current Law</i> 
is being offered as a solution with less frequency.
<p>
<li>This language was drafted primarily by Professor Michael McConnell of 
the University of Chicago School of Law and Steven McFarland of the 
Christian Legal Society, and submitted to the Committee on October 20, 1995.
<p>
<li><i>U.S.</i>, No. 94-329, 1995 U.S. LEXIS 4461 (U.S. 1995).
<p>
<li><i>Id</i>.
<p>
<li><i>Id</i>. (O'Connor, J., concurring).
<p>
<li>330 U.S. 1 (1947).
<p>
