Approach to Distinctively Christian Education</I>.  Wheaton, Ill.:
 Crossway Books, 1991.
<P>
Wilson, Douglas, Wesley Callihan, and Douglas Jones<I>.  Classical
Education and the Home School</I>.  Moscow, Idaho:  Canon Press,
1995.  (800) 488-2034
<P>
<I>Trivium Pursuit Magazine</I>, 139 Colorado St., Suite 168,
Muscatine, Iowa 52761.
<P>
<I>Practical Homeschooling</I>, P.O. Box 1250, Fenton, Mo.  63026.
 Phone:  (800) 346-6322. 
